==Gamilaraay==
{{wikipedia|Australian Aboriginal kinship}}
===Noun===
{{head|kld|noun}}
# A female [[marriage class]] or [[skin group]]. A ''yibathaa'' can marry only a {{m|kld|gabi}}; her sons will be {{m|kld|gambu}}, and her daughters {{m|kld|buuthaa}}.
